# Third-Party Sources

This package bundles or depends on the following third-party components.

## Qt
- Source releases: https://download.qt.io/official_releases/qt/
- Debian/Ubuntu package source: use `apt source qt6-base`, `apt source qt6-declarative`, and related Qt 6 source packages for the target distribution.

## FFmpeg
- Debian/Ubuntu package source: use `apt source ffmpeg` for the target distribution.
- Upstream source: https://github.com/FFmpeg/FFmpeg

